data.text: Update: Definitely experienced the expected side effects of an immunization shot. Chills, low grade fever & aches at the joints which only lasted about 8-10 hrs start to finish.  It was no worse than what I experienced when I got my flu shot. Feeling good now.  #GetVaccinated

So far, I’m only experiencing soreness at the injection site which is to be expected.  I am prepared for symptoms (aches and low grade fever) similar to what one would get after getting an flu shot.  #GetVaccinated #didmyresearch
